{"word":"Ephod","slug":"ephod","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ephod</b> <a href=\"#/H641\">H641</a> <br/> 1. A sacred vestment worn by the high priest<br/> - Described<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=14'>Exo 28:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=35'>Exo 28:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=25&verse=7'>Exo 25:7</a> <br/> - Making of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=26'>Exo 39:26</a> <br/> - Breastplate attached to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=29'>Exo 28:29</a> <br/> - Worn by Aaron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=5'>Exo 39:5</a> <br/> - Used as an oracle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=23&verse=9'>1Sa 23:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=23&verse=12'>1Sa 23:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=30&verse=8'>1Sa 30:8</a> <br/> - An inferior, was worn:<br/> b by the common priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=18'>1Sa 22:18</a><br/> b by Samuel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=2&verse=18'>1Sa 2:18</a><br/> b by David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=14'>2Sa 6:14</a><br/> - It was called Coat<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=40'>Exo 28:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=8'>Exo 29:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=27'>Exo 39:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=14'>Exo 40:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=13'>Lev 8:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=5'>Lev 10:5</a> <br/> - Made by Gideon, became an idolatrous snare to Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=27'>Jdg 8:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=17&verse=5'>Jdg 17:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=18&verse=14'>Jdg 18:14</a> <br/> - Prophecy concerning the absence of the Ephod from Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=3&verse=4'>Hos 3:4</a> <br/> 2. A man of Manasseh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=34&verse=23'>Num 34:23</a>"}]}